---

<Base
  title={title}
  description={metaDescription}
  canonical={canonical}
>
  <script slot="schema" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(localBusinessSchema)} />
  <script slot="schema" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(serviceSchema)} />

  <Header slot="header" />

  <div class="container py-6">
    <Breadcrumbs
      items={[
        { label: "Kitchen Fitter Kenilworth", href: "/kitchen-fitter-kenilworth/" },
      ]}
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-5 leading-tight" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Kitchen Fitter Kenilworth — Independent Kitchen Installation by Pindi Sahota
        </h1>
        <AnswerBlock
          answer="Pindi Sahota is an independent kitchen fitter serving Kenilworth and the CV8 postcode. With 30 years of experience — including premium large-format installations in Kenilworth's substantial detached homes — he delivers the exceptional standard of finish that Kenilworth homeowners expect. Fixed-price quotes guaranteed after a £195 pre-installation survey, credited back on booking."
        />
        <KeyTakeaway points={takeawayPoints} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Photo Gallery -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: var(--navy);">
        Kitchen Installations in Kenilworth
      </h2>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <figure class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/assets/kitchen-fitter/kitchen-fitter-kenilworth-white-gloss-granite-island-warwickshire-3024x4032.webp"
            alt="Kitchen fitter Kenilworth — white gloss kitchen with granite island installed in Kenilworth, Warwickshire"
            width="3024"
            height="4032"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="gallery-img"
          />
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/assets/kitchen-fitter/kitchen-fitter-kenilworth-sage-green-shaker-oak-worktop-installation-4032x3024.webp"
            alt="Kitchen fitter Kenilworth — sage green shaker kitchen with solid oak worktop fitted in Kenilworth CV8"
            width="4032"
            height="3024"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="gallery-img"
          />
        </figure>
        <figure class="gallery-item">
          <img
            src="/assets/kitchen-fitter/kitchen-fitter-kenilworth-grey-handleless-kitchen-installation-3024x4032.webp"
            alt="Kitchen fitter Kenilworth — grey handleless kitchen installation in Kenilworth, Warwickshire"
            width="3024"
            height="4032"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            class="gallery-img"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: Independent vs Retailer Fitters -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Independent Kitchen Fitter vs Retailer Fitter — Why It Matters More in Kenilworth
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          For a straightforward budget kitchen, the difference between an independent fitter and a retailer's installation scheme may be modest. For a premium kitchen in a Kenilworth home — a 22-unit layout with a quartz island, integrated Neff appliances, and handleless cabinetry — the difference is significant.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Retailer-scheme fitters work to a pace set by the retailer's margin, not your expectations. An independent fitter like Pindi Sahota works directly for you, at a pace that allows every door alignment, every worktop join, and every appliance panel reveal to be set to the highest standard. There is no call centre between you and the person doing the work, and no incentive to move on to the next job before yours is exactly right.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Independence also means impartiality. Pindi is not tied to any retailer, which means he can advise you honestly on what he has found in practice — what installs well, what requires additional care, and what to watch for — rather than being limited to promoting the products of one supply chain.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          For Kenilworth homeowners investing in a premium kitchen, working with an independent fitter who has deep experience in the town is the most reliable way to ensure the finished result matches the investment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Why Kenilworth Homeowners Choose Pindi -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Why Kenilworth Homeowners Choose Pindi Sahota
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi Sahota has been fitting kitchens in Kenilworth for many years and understands the town's property character in detail. He is based at 242 Hollyfast Road, Coundon, Coventry CV6 2AH — approximately 8 miles north of Kenilworth — and serves the CV8 postcode area as a matter of routine.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Kenilworth is one of Warwickshire's most affluent towns, and its housing stock reflects this. Along Coventry Road and Castle Road you find large Victorian and Edwardian detached houses with high ceilings, ornate architectural details, and spacious kitchen footprints. In Beehive Hill, Whitemoor, and the newer developments, modern executive homes offer open-plan kitchen-diner-living configurations that demand precise planning and flawless execution. Edwardian semis and 1930s substantial detached properties fill the space in between — all requiring different approaches to levelling, plumbing routes, and unit configuration.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Kenilworth kitchens are typically larger than the regional average. Island installations, full-height larder towers, integrated wine coolers and warming drawers, stone or solid timber worktops — these are commonplace rather than exceptional. Getting every element of a large installation right requires a fitter who has done it many times before and has the patience to set each stage correctly rather than rushing to completion.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi has fitted the Wren Infinity Plus handleless kitchen in Kenilworth — the installation that features as the Wren case study on the Install My Kitchen website. It is representative of the standard he delivers across the town. See the <a href="/projects/wren-kitchen-kenilworth/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">Kenilworth Wren project page</a> for photos and details.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: The Survey-First Process -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          The Survey-First Process — How It Works
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Every kitchen fitting project begins with a pre-installation survey, carried out by Pindi personally. The survey costs £195 and is credited back in full if you go ahead with the installation. For a large Kenilworth kitchen, this survey is especially valuable: the complexity of a 20-plus-unit installation with an island, stone worktops, and integrated appliances means there are many more variables to plan for — and any missed at this stage will cost more to resolve mid-installation.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          During the survey, Pindi takes precise room measurements, checks ceiling heights and wall angles, inspects existing plumbing and electrics routes, reviews your kitchen plan and elevation drawings in detail, and identifies any work that will need to happen before or alongside the installation. For Kenilworth's larger Victorian and Edwardian properties, this often includes discussion of structural walls, ceiling height variations from period cornicing, and whether any underfloor adjustment is needed ahead of installation.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          After the survey you receive a written, fixed-price quote. The price does not change unless you change the scope of work. There are no estimates and no retrospective charges for complications that should have been spotted in advance.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Survey appointments in Kenilworth are typically available within two weeks. To book, call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> or visit the <a href="/survey/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">survey booking page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Retailers -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Which Kitchen Brands Does Pindi Fit in Kenilworth?
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Because Pindi is fully independent, he can fit kitchens purchased from any retailer or manufacturer. In Kenilworth, where homeowners often invest at the premium end of the market, the most common kitchens he installs include:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 pl-1" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Wren Kitchens</strong> — including the Infinity Plus handleless range, which Pindi has fitted in Kenilworth. See the <a href="/retailers/wren/" style="color: var(--teal);">Wren installation page</a> and the <a href="/projects/wren-kitchen-kenilworth/" style="color: var(--teal);">Kenilworth case study</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Howdens Joinery</strong> — Pindi has a trade account with Howdens, giving him direct depot access for components and fixings. See the <a href="/retailers/howdens/" style="color: var(--teal);">Howdens installation page</a>.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Magnet and Kutchenhaus</strong> — both popular choices for Kenilworth homeowners seeking mid-to-premium quality British-designed kitchens.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Häcker and Nobilia</strong> — leading German manufacturers commonly chosen for their engineering precision and contemporary aesthetics; regularly fitted in Kenilworth's modern executive homes.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>Mereway, Neptune, and deVOL</strong> — premium British brands favoured in Kenilworth's period properties; Pindi handles these with the meticulous attention to detail their quality demands.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span><strong>IKEA, Wickes, B&Q, Benchmarx, DIY Kitchens, Symphony, Masterclass</strong> — all fitted to the same high standard regardless of price point.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          If your kitchen brand is not listed, call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> — in almost every case it can be accommodated.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <SupplierLogos />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Areas Covered -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Areas of Kenilworth and CV8 Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi covers the whole of the CV8 postcode area, with regular work across all parts of Kenilworth and the surrounding villages. He regularly installs kitchens in:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Kenilworth Town</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Kenilworth town centre</strong> — period and modern properties in the heart of the town</li>
              <li><strong>Castle Road</strong> — prestigious Victorian and Edwardian detached homes</li>
              <li><strong>Beehive Hill</strong> — modern executive development with larger open-plan kitchens</li>
              <li><strong>Crackley</strong> — established residential area bordering the town's north edge</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Surrounding Villages</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Burton Green</strong> — village west of Kenilworth, mix of period and modern properties</li>
              <li><strong>Balsall Common</strong> — nearby village just beyond CV8, also covered</li>
              <li>All CV8 postcodes covered as standard</li>
              <li>Wider Warwickshire coverage available — call to confirm</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Visit the <a href="/areas/kenilworth/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">Kenilworth area page</a> for more detailed information, or call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> to confirm your postcode is covered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: What's Included & Pricing -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          What's Included in a Kitchen Fit — and How Pricing Works
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          A full kitchen fitting service from Pindi Sahota covers the complete installation from stripped room to finished kitchen. In Kenilworth, this typically means larger-scale, more complex projects, but the scope is the same: every component is included in the fixed price established at survey stage.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 pl-1" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Stripping out the existing kitchen, including disconnecting the sink and removing all appliances</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Levelling and setting out all base units — precision-critical in Kenilworth's period properties where floors may have settled unevenly over decades</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Fitting all wall and base carcasses, doors, drawers, hinges, and soft-close mechanisms — with alignments set to the highest standard of finish</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Island installation including structural securing, carcass building, and integrated storage configuration</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Cutting and fitting stone, quartz, solid timber, or laminate worktops — including joints routed and sealed to an invisible standard</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Sink and tap installation, including connection to existing waste and supply pipework</span>
          </li>
